    "synopsis": "Eight short stories that move through the Great Crusade and the years that bend toward the Heresy, each one circling a different primarch. A young Ferrus Manus crash-lands in perpetual gloom; Mortarion tries to redeem the slaughter on Galaspar with a fresh compliance and finds treachery instead; Jaghatai Khan outmanoeuvres an Iron Warriors warsmith; a Blood Angel sets out to capture beauty in a galaxy at war; a remembrancer rides with Konrad Curze and learns what compliance under the Night Lords really costs; Roboute Guilliman returns to a restless Macragge; Rogal Dorn investigates strange deaths inside the Imperial Palace on the eve of the Siege; and Dark Angels make first contact with Alpharius during the Rangdan Xenocides.",
